casebody.data:
No. 09-9487. Anthony Grant Jackson, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 1128, 131 S. Ct. 896,

178 L. Ed. 2d 739,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 126. January 10, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit for further consideration in light of Johnson v. United States, 559 U.S. 133, 130 S. Ct. 1265, 176 L. Ed. 2d 1 (2010).

Same case below, 355 Fed. Appx. 297.
